quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On Tippin…óo e dow Jeyaa…óo Makko on Deftere nden O wa…óanaali nde oo√±aare"
  18,2,"Feewunde fii yo o [Nulaa…óo on] hul…ìinir lepte sattu…óe immorde ka Makko o weltinira gom…óin…ìe …ìen, …ìen …ìe no golla Mo∆¥∆¥u…ói …óin wonnde no woodani …ìe Njoddi Mo∆¥∆¥iri"
  18,3,"Ko …ìe √±ii…ìoo…ìe e nder makko [Neema on] poomaa"
  18,4,"O rentina …ìen wi\"u…ìe: \"Alla jogitike …ìi…ó…óo"
  18,5,"Ganndal alanaa…ìe e mun, wanaa baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe woodani, mawnii konngol wonungol e yaltude e kunndu…óe ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wowlaali si wanaa fenaande"
  18,6,"Bala jo'o an a tanpinay hoore-maa e dow batteeji ma…ì…ìe, si gom…óinaali ndee Yewtere ka suno"
  18,7,"Menen Men wa…óii ko woni kon ka hoore leydi cu…óaari mayri, fii yo Men jarribo …ìe ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe …ìurata mo∆¥∆¥innde golle"
  18,8,Menen ko Men wa…óoo…ìe ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol yoorungal
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yim…ìe fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi …óin, …óun wonu immorde e Aayeeje Amen hawnii…óe"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaa…ìe …ìen sorunoo ka fammeere, …ìe wi'i: \"Joomi amen okku men immorde ka Maa…óa Hinnayee=yurmeende newinaNaa men kadi e fiyaake amen peewal"
  18,11,Men piyi e dow noppi ma…ì…ìe …óin ka nder fammeere limoore duu…ìi
  18,12,"Refti Men immintini …ìe fii yo Men fen√±inir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle …óen …ói…ói …ìuri moftude [limoore] ko …ìe √±ii…ìi kon dummunne"